### API Testing Endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ==============================
### User Endpoints
### ==============================

### Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/user

### Get user by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

### Create user
POST {{baseUrl}}/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Update user
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/user/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Smith"
}

### Delete user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

